    "Fig. 8 A graph with environmental and human factors impacting thermal comfort for making a model and predicting the thermal preference.",
    "Source: [77]In turn, energy market participation can be regarded as part of the personalization of smart building energy utilization.",
    "For instance, blockchains that can be utilized for decentralized energy trading and that fulfill privacy, security and trust objectives [154] (See Fig. 9).",
